=========================================================
INGESTION LAMBDA
=========================================================

Lambda receives sensor readings.

Responsibilities:

1. Validate payload
2. Normalize timestamp
3. Identify tenant using device registry
4. Write to time-series database
5. Store raw data in data lake
6. Trigger analytics pipeline


Pseudo workflow:

receive_event()

validate_schema()

lookup_device_registry()

write_to_timestream()

store_raw_to_s3()

publish_event_for_analytics()


