=========================================================
ANALYTICS PROCESSING
=========================================================

Analytics processor runs on new sensor events.

Processing tasks:

rolling average
temperature trend
anomaly detection


Rolling window example:

rolling_avg_10min


Rate of temperature change:

temp(t) - temp(t-5min)


=========================================================
ANOMALY DETECTION
=========================================================

Use lightweight statistical models.

Method 1: Z-score

z = (temp - mean) / std

If:

abs(z) > 3

Trigger anomaly.


Method 2: Moving Average Deviation

if:

current_temp > rolling_mean + threshold


=========================================================
FORECASTING MODELS
=========================================================

Models must be lightweight.

Recommended models:

ARIMA
Facebook Prophet
Exponential Smoothing


Model characteristics:

low compute
fast inference
good for time series


Forecast outputs:

temperature next 30 minutes
temperature next 2 hours
temperature next 24 hours


Forecast execution schedule:

every 15 minutes
or
hourly


=========================================================
ALERT ENGINE
=========================================================

Alerts generated when conditions met.

Alert Types:

HIGH TEMPERATURE

temperature > 85°F
duration > 10 minutes


RAPID TEMPERATURE INCREASE

temperature increase > 4°F
within 10 minutes


SENSOR OFFLINE

no reading received for 60 seconds


LOW BATTERY

power < 20%


Alerts sent via:

SNS
email
SMS
webhook


